2k8H0r8rDK4bx0uh8gRkLcM1560955525923compressflag.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F0RxDGELgui9PQ16PbJjDJz2k8H0r8rDK4bx0uh8gRkLcM1560955525923compressflag.jpg&h=b3e990b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n長河東流，唯一正面講述南明歷史電視劇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"727ae5f5a9c95ec933e4eb18d6f5976b978f0baf","tid":1982703,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"923aa59c2144cd7557ae59cdcdf2592e33c3d631","tid":1982703,"uid":109437,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T11:43:27.000Z","msg":"收到風5月8開關"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T12:17:10.000Z","msg":"合理"},{"pid":"394ed51f57916aa3508ced5f47f395b8810d5f49","tid":1982703,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T12:24:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f30ee63d3aa7ac2e8c26bded86f63b48bcfb6e9","tid":1982703,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T13:33:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad115b8c6b53a88d1d33c5569195f8daf8de4fe2","tid":1982703,"uid":281023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T13:46:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6fe8215c9ed7011a34c51f08dc81c698e12846f5","tid":1982703,"uid":281023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T13:47:08.000Z","msg":"大陸點解要d蝗蟲落黎先<br />\n唔係應該tum香港人上去刺激消費咩"},{"pid":"419e0a19afd6a726ac8edcd9296b150404fce872","tid":1982703,"uid":34899,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T15:22:06.000Z","msg":"支持厚巴<br />\n<br />\n病毒是醫學<br />\n抗疫是政治"},{"pid":"dcfaad234b799517da83d6a84aecc932cac69333","tid":1982703,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T15:24:02.000Z","msg":"屌奶星我記錯限舖令(599F)章號都冇人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36c308f7330490e1f95293b3c89d5b506cc3517f","tid":1982703,"uid":5026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T15:26:10.000Z","msg":"一切都係港共預訂好晒"}],"pinned":{"pid":"d2ebfd83f70b23b1ff6606cdfe0f0b097df68fdf","tid":1982703,"uid":7439,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T11:04:16.000Z","msg":"屌哂你地老母 真係冇人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}}